{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.1","label":"","reference":"Esdras 3:1","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.002.070,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.003.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">L\u2019autel des holocaustes r\u00e9tabli<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-7: cf. De 12:11-14. (L\u00e9 23:33-36, 39-43. N\u00e9 8:13-18.) Ps 107.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.3.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Le septi\u00e8me mois arriva, et les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl \u00e9taient dans leurs villes. Alors le peuple s\u2019assembla comme un seul homme \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3","name":"Esdras 3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3.2","name":"Esdras 3:2","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.2.70","name":"Esdras 2:70","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.2.70"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.2","label":"","reference":"Esdras 3:2","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.003.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.003.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.3.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Josu\u00e9, fils de Jotsadak, avec ses fr\u00e8res les sacrificateurs, et Zorobabel, fils de Schealthiel, avec ses fr\u00e8res, se lev\u00e8rent et b\u00e2tirent l\u2019autel du Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, pour y offrir des holocaustes, selon ce qui est \u00e9crit dans la loi de Mo\u00efse, homme de Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3","name":"Esdras 3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3.3","name":"Esdras 3:3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3.1","name":"Esdras 3:1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.3","label":"","reference":"Esdras 3:3","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.003.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.003.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.3.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Ils r\u00e9tablirent l\u2019autel sur ses fondements, quoiqu\u2019ils eussent \u00e0 craindre les peuples du pays, et ils y offrirent des holocaustes \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, les holocaustes du matin et du soir.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3","name":"Esdras 3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3.4","name":"Esdras 3:4","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3.2","name":"Esdras 3:2","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.4","label":"","reference":"Esdras 3:4","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.003.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.003.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.3.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Ils c\u00e9l\u00e9br\u00e8rent la f\u00eate des tabernacles, comme il est \u00e9crit, et ils offrirent jour par jour des holocaustes, selon le nombre ordonn\u00e9 pour chaque jour.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3","name":"Esdras 3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3.5","name":"Esdras 3:5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3.3","name":"Esdras 3:3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.5","label":"","reference":"Esdras 3:5","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.003.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.003.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.3.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Apr\u00e8s cela, ils offrirent l\u2019holocauste perp\u00e9tuel, les holocaustes des nouvelles lunes et de toutes les solennit\u00e9s consacr\u00e9es \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et ceux de quiconque faisait des offrandes volontaires \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3","name":"Esdras 3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3.6","name":"Esdras 3:6","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3.4","name":"Esdras 3:4","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.6","label":"","reference":"Esdras 3:6","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.003.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.003.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.3.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>D\u00e8s le premier jour du septi\u00e8me mois, ils commenc\u00e8rent \u00e0 offrir \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel des holocaustes. Cependant les fondements du temple de l\u2019\u00c9ternel n\u2019\u00e9taient pas encore pos\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3","name":"Esdras 3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3.7","name":"Esdras 3:7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3.5","name":"Esdras 3:5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.7","label":"","reference":"Esdras 3:7","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.003.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.003.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.3.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>On donna de l\u2019argent aux tailleurs de pierres et aux charpentiers, et des vivres, des boissons et de l\u2019huile aux Sidoniens et aux Tyriens, pour qu\u2019ils amenassent par mer jusqu\u2019\u00e0 Japho des bois de c\u00e8dre du Liban, suivant l\u2019autorisation qu\u2019on avait eue de Cyrus, roi de Perse.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3","name":"Esdras 3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3.8","name":"Esdras 3:8","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3.6","name":"Esdras 3:6","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.8","label":"","reference":"Esdras 3:8","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.003.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.003.009,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Les fondements du temple pos\u00e9s<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 8-13: cf. (1 R 6:1-3.) Ps 118.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.3.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>La seconde ann\u00e9e depuis leur arriv\u00e9e \u00e0 la maison de Dieu \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, au second mois, Zorobabel, fils de Schealthiel, Josu\u00e9, fils de Jotsadak, avec le reste de leurs fr\u00e8res les sacrificateurs et les L\u00e9vites, et tous ceux qui \u00e9taient revenus de la captivit\u00e9 \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, se mirent \u00e0 l\u2019\u0153uvre et charg\u00e8rent les L\u00e9vites de vingt ans et au-dessus de surveiller les travaux de la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3","name":"Esdras 3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3.9","name":"Esdras 3:9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3.7","name":"Esdras 3:7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.9","label":"","reference":"Esdras 3:9","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.003.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.003.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.3.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Et Josu\u00e9, avec ses fils et ses fr\u00e8res, Kadmiel, avec ses fils, fils de Juda, les fils de H\u00e9nadad, avec leurs fils et leurs fr\u00e8res les L\u00e9vites, se pr\u00e9par\u00e8rent tous ensemble \u00e0 surveiller ceux qui travaillaient \u00e0 la maison de Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3","name":"Esdras 3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3.10","name":"Esdras 3:10","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3.8","name":"Esdras 3:8","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.10","label":"","reference":"Esdras 3:10","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.003.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.003.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.3.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Lorsque les ouvriers pos\u00e8rent les fondements du temple de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, on fit assister les sacrificateurs en costume, avec les trompettes, et les L\u00e9vites, fils d\u2019Asaph, avec les cymbales, afin qu\u2019ils c\u00e9l\u00e9brassent l\u2019\u00c9ternel, d\u2019apr\u00e8s les ordonnances de David, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3","name":"Esdras 3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3.11","name":"Esdras 3:11","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3.9","name":"Esdras 3:9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.11","label":"","reference":"Esdras 3:11","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.003.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.003.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.3.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Ils chantaient, c\u00e9l\u00e9brant et louant l\u2019\u00c9ternel par ces paroles: Car il est bon, car sa mis\u00e9ricorde pour Isra\u00ebl dure \u00e0 toujours! Et tout le peuple poussait de grands cris de joie en c\u00e9l\u00e9brant l\u2019\u00c9ternel, parce qu\u2019on posait les fondements de la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3","name":"Esdras 3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3.12","name":"Esdras 3:12","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3.10","name":"Esdras 3:10","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.12","label":"","reference":"Esdras 3:12","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.003.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.003.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.3.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Mais plusieurs des sacrificateurs et des L\u00e9vites, et des chefs de famille \u00e2g\u00e9s, qui avaient vu la premi\u00e8re maison, pleuraient \u00e0 grand bruit pendant qu\u2019on posait sous leurs yeux les fondements de cette maison. Beaucoup d\u2019autres faisaient \u00e9clater leur joie par des cris,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3","name":"Esdras 3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3.13","name":"Esdras 3:13","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3.11","name":"Esdras 3:11","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.13","label":"","reference":"Esdras 3:13","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.003.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.004.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.3.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>en sorte qu\u2019on ne pouvait distinguer le bruit des cris de joie d\u2019avec le bruit des pleurs parmi le peuple, car le peuple poussait de grands cris dont le son s\u2019entendait au loin.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3","name":"Esdras 3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.4.1","name":"Esdras 4:1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.4.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.3.12","name":"Esdras 3:12","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.3.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb4b85774.76716593');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb4b85774.76716593\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb4b85774.76716593","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb4b85774.76716593'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb4b85774.76716593\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}